This directory is intended for project-specific (private) libraries.

PlatformIO compiles them to static libraries and links them into the executable.

Each library should be placed in its own subdirectory, for example:

    lib/my_library/my_library.h
    lib/my_library/my_library.cpp

More information about PlatformIO library dependency finder:
https://docs.platformio.org/page/librarymanager/ldf.html
